&lt;li class=&quot;_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM&quot;&gt;Allah turns them into scum¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://quranx.com/23.41&quot;&gt;23.41&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
