&lt;td style=&quot;width: 99.5519%; height: 182.523px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Divine_Revelation_OR_Human_Drama&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #e03e2d;&quot;&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;color: #e03e2d;&quot; href=&quot;https://sachaai.com/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama&quot;&gt;Flawless divine revelation or merely a flawed human drama?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #e03e2d;&quot;&gt;The question at hand is whether Islam represents a flawless divine revelation or merely a flawed human drama. By examining its content, one can determine its true nature and discern whether it bears the marks of divine wisdom or human fallibility. Take the time to read and reflect in order to arrive at your own conclusion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
