&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #e03e2d;&quot;&gt;A huge conflict exists between humanity and religion, particularly concerning the matter of Islamic Slavery. This is a crucial issue that led many Muslims to doubt and question Islam and finally to abandon it and become ex-Muslims.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
